{"ts": "2026-06-09T00:02:47.821491+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "[{\"number\":1,\"title\":\"Add TF-IDF normalization to the vectorizer pipeline\",\"body\":\"Adds the L2 normalization step to the `TfidfTransformer` used by the 20-newsgroups classifier so each document\\u0026#39;s tf-idf vector has unit norm before being fed to the downstream MultinomialNB / SVM classifiers.\\n\\n- `TfidfTransformer(norm=\\u0026#39;l2\\u0026#39;, sublinear_tf=False)` (was previously left at defaults — `norm=\\u0026#39;l2\\u0026#39;` is also the default, but stating it explicitly makes the pipeline self-documenting and lets us change `sublinear_tf` later without surprises).\\n- No model or scoring change expected; this is a \\u0026#34;make the implicit explicit\\u0026#34; PR ahead of the upcoming `sublinear_tf=True` experiment.\\n\\nSmoke tested by running the example training script — accuracy unchanged at 77.4% on the 20-newsgroups test set.\\n\",\"state\":\"open\",\"draft\":false,\"merged\":false,\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/rpnr-bench/T08_R02/pull/1\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"SjJ1017\",\"id\":100460031,\"profile_url\":\"https://github.com/SjJ1017\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/100460031?v=4\"},\"head\":{\"ref\":\"feature/tfidf-normalization-t08_r02\",\"sha\":\"43dc5c0eb0a352c377b97795cf2575e9e8e6e071\",\"repo\":{\"full_name\":\"rpnr-bench/T08_R02\",\"description\":\"Machine learning with text using Multinomial Naive Bayes, SVM and other classifiers from scikit-learn.\"}},\"base\":{\"ref\":\"main\",\"sha\":\"9f3ac6c474f7b2d71649cfdb19596e6fc78c5586\",\"repo\":{\"full_name\":\"rpnr-bench/T08_R02\",\"description\":\"Machine learning with text using Multinomial Naive Bayes, SVM and other classifiers from scikit-learn.\"}},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-19T23:37:59Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-22T09:52:18Z\"}]", "id": "lc_c33e02ce-ee5f-4413-b928-43dbf361ebb9"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "r